      • createReactiveHealthIndicatorRegistry

        public ReactiveHealthIndicatorRegistry createReactiveHealthIndicatorRegistry(Map<String,ReactiveHealthIndicator> reactiveHealthIndicators,
                                                                             Map<String,HealthIndicator> healthIndicators)
        Deprecated. 
        Create a ReactiveHealthIndicatorRegistry based on the specified health indicators. Each HealthIndicator are wrapped to a HealthIndicatorReactiveAdapter. If two instances share the same name, the reactive variant takes precedence.
        Parameters:
        reactiveHealthIndicators - the ReactiveHealthIndicator instances mapped by name
        healthIndicators - the HealthIndicator instances mapped by name if any.
        Returns:
        a ReactiveHealthIndicator that delegates to the specified reactiveHealthIndicators.
